2006年9月1日，[[巴西奥林匹克委员会|巴西奥林匹克委员会]]宣布[[里约热内卢|里约热内卢]]申办第三十一届夏季奥林匹克运动会<ref name="BOC 1">{{cite web|url=http://www.cob.org.br/noticias/noticias_interna.asp?id=4584|title=Rio is the Brazilian applicant city for the 2016 Summer Olympics|author=Brazilian Olympic Committee|date=2006-09-01|accessdate=2009-09-20|language=pt|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100213025456/http://www.cob.org.br/noticias/noticias_interna.asp?id=4584|archivedate=2010-02-13}}</ref>。这是该城市自[[1936年夏季奥林匹克运动会|1936年]]、[[1940年夏季奥林匹克运动会|1940年]]、[[2004年夏季奥林匹克运动会|2004年]]和[[2012年夏季奥林匹克运动会|2012年]]的四次失利后，首次进入资格候选阶段<ref name="GB 2">{{cite web | title = Rio de Janeiro, Brazil | work = Bid city profile and Fact sheet | publisher = GamesBids.com | url = http://www.gamesbids.com/english/bids/rio2016.shtml | accessdate = 2008-07-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080509074745/http://www.gamesbids.com/english/bids/rio2016.shtml | archive-date = 2008-05-09 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。里约将成为首个举办该赛事的巴西和南美城市<ref name="AP">{{cite news | last = Wilson | first = Stephen | title = IOC picks Chicago among 4 finalists for 2016 Games | publisher = The Associated Press | date = 2008-06-04 | url = http://ap.google.com/article/ALeqM5gCXx3AcQIf0F9QkvGABKYylcGhpAD913GI0O0 | accessdate = 2008-06-04 }}{{dead link|date=October 2012|bot=Legobot}}</ref>。里约计划在城市里举办所有项目，给赛事带来动感，增加运动员的互动<ref name="Rio project">{{cite web | title = Project | work = Rio 2016 | publisher = Rio de Janeiro 2016 Summer Olympics bid official website | url = http://www.rio2016.org.br/en/Rio2016/Projeto.aspx | accessdate = 2008-07-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080405163922/http://www.rio2016.org.br/en/Rio2016/Projeto.aspx | archivedate = 2008-04-05 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。其中，将在[[巴拉_(里约热内卢)|巴拉]]、[[科帕卡瓦纳_(里约热内卢)|科帕卡瓦纳]]、[[德奥多罗_(里约热内卢)|德奥多罗]]和[[马拉卡纳_(里约热内卢)|马拉卡纳]]四个奥运会园区设立七个比赛场馆<ref>{{cite web | title = Sites | work = Rio 2016 | publisher = Rio de Janeiro 2016 Summer Olympics bid official website | url = http://www.rio2016.org.br/en/Rio2016/Locais.aspx | accessdate = 2008-07-03 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080131150944/http://www.rio2016.org.br/en/Rio2016/Locais.aspx | archivedate = 2008-01-31 }}</ref>，而足球比赛将在[[贝洛奥里藏特|贝洛奥里藏特]]、[[巴西利亚|巴西利亚]]、[[萨尔瓦多|萨尔瓦多]]和[[圣保罗|圣保罗]]等城市举行<ref name="Bid book">{{cite book | title = Candidature Acceptance Application | publisher = Brazilian Olympic Committee | date = 2008-01-14 | url = http://www.rio2016.org.br/util/pdf/rio2016.pdf | format = PDF | accessdate = 2008-07-03 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090320033430/http://www.rio2016.org.br/util/pdf/rio2016.pdf | archivedate = 2009-03-20 }}</ref>。奥运赛事预定日期为8月5日到8月21日，残奥运会日期则为9月7日（巴西[[独立日|独立日]]）到9月18日<ref name="Rio project"/>。里约热内卢在以前的申请中落败的原因，主要在于缺乏基础设施、安保和组织国际体育赛事的经验。巴西曾主办[[1950年世界杯足球赛|1950年世界杯足球赛]]，里约是比赛城市之一和决赛地点，尽管有过数次改革，但随着时间的推移，结构已经退化。然而，里约在2007年7月13日到7月29日举办了[[2007年泛美运动会|第十五届泛美运动会]]，让城市从失败中复苏<ref>{{cite web | title = Pan Am Games Could Make Rio Strong Olympic Games Candidate – Rogge | work = 2016 Summer Olympic bids | publisher = GamesBids.com | url = http://www.gamesbids.com/cgi-bin/news/viewnews.cgi?category=1&id=1184345120 | accessdate = 2008-07-16 }}</ref>。[[泛美体育组织|泛美体育组织]]主席马里奥·巴斯克斯·拉纳在闭幕式演讲中盛赞本届赛事是该项赛事史上办得最好的一届<ref name="Raña">{{cite news | title = Rio stages gala ending for Pan American Games | publisher = The International Herald Tribune | date = 2007-07-29 | url = http://www.iht.com/articles/ap/2007/07/29/sports/LA-SPT-Pan-Ams-Closing-Ceremonies.php | accessdate = 2008-07-01 | archive-date = 2008-05-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080506191143/http://www.iht.com/articles/ap/2007/07/29/sports/LA-SPT-Pan-Ams-Closing-Ceremonies.php | dead-url = no }}</ref>。巴西在[[2014年世界杯足球赛|2014年再次举办世界杯]]，给第二次举办赛事决赛的里约带来更多的经验<ref>{{cite web | title = Brazil Submits 2014 World Cup Bid Ahead Of 2016 Olympic Bid | work = 2016 Summer Olympic bids | publisher = GamesBids.com | url = http://www.gamesbids.com/cgi-bin/news/viewnews.cgi?category=1&id=1185898110 | accessdate = 2008-07-16 | archive-date = 2007-12-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20071215025737/http://www.gamesbids.com/cgi-bin/news/viewnews.cgi?category=1&id=1185898110 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。里约热内卢奥林匹克组织委员会表示，整座城市将改造成一个用于庆祝这一体育盛事的奥运剧场<ref name="Rio project"/>。里约的地形补充了紧凑的空间，包含七个坐落在四个奥运园区——巴拉、科帕卡瓦纳、德奥多罗和马拉卡纳的比赛场馆，全部位于城市内。概念中心区巴拉是该城市较新和发展最快的地区，由山地、海滩和泻湖构成<ref name="CAA 3">{{cite book | title = Candidature Acceptance Application | quote = Venues | publisher = Brazilian Olympic Committee | date = 2008-01-14 | url = http://www.rio2016.org.br/util/pdf/rio2016.pdf | pages = 15–17 | format = PDF | accessdate = 2008-07-20 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090320033430/http://www.rio2016.org.br/util/pdf/rio2016.pdf | archivedate = 2009-03-20 }}</ref>。申办标志于2007年12月17日在[[里约热内卢市立剧院|里约热内卢市立剧院]]举行的巴西奥运奖颁奖典礼上揭晓，该标志被委员会选入最终四强<ref>{{cite web | title = Rio 2016 Launches Bid Logo | work = 2016 Summer Olympic bids | publisher = GamesBids.com | url = http://www.gamesbids.com/cgi-bin/news/viewnews.cgi?category=1&id=1197932561 | accessdate = 2008-07-16 }}</ref>。巴西奥委会选用里约最突出的标志[[糖面包山|糖面包山]]（{{lang-pt|Pão de Açucar}}）作为标志<ref name="Rio look">{{cite web | title = Look of the Bid | work = Rio 2016 | publisher = Rio de Janeiro 2016 Summer Olympics bid official website | url = http://www.rio2016.org.br/en/Rio2016/Visual.aspx | accessdate = 2008-07-16 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080829161858/http://www.rio2016.org.br/en/Rio2016/Visual.aspx | archivedate = 2008-08-29 }}</ref>。该景观呈心形，反过来代表着巴西不容置疑的热情和对赛事的积极<ref name="Rio look"/>。
